                        <date notBefore="1500" notAfter="1599"/>
                        <desc><persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS9602Turaev">Boris Turaev</persName> indicates that the handwriting is careful, large, datable to the 16th century. <persName role="scribe" cert="low" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11482Yohannes">Yoḥannǝs</persName> was possibly the scribe.</desc>
                     </handNote>
